Package net.apartium.cocoabeans.collect

Class WeightSet<E>

java.lang.Object
net.apartium.cocoabeans.collect.WeightSet<E>
Type Parameters:
E - element type
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Set<E>
public class WeightSet<E> extends Object implements Set<E>
A set implementation with weighted keys This class is not thread safe.
